        "pid": "168180055",
        "id": "note27",
        "text": "<p data-aid=\"168180451\" id=\"p_sWLb2\">\u201cThe first great <em>commandment<\/em> of all eternity is to love God with all of <em>our<\/em> heart, might, mind, and strength\u2014that\u2019s the first great commandment. But the first great <em>truth<\/em> of all eternity is that God loves <em>us<\/em> with all of <em>His<\/em> heart, might, mind, and strength\u201d (Jeffrey R. Holland, \u201c<a class=\"cross-ref\" href=\"/study/general-conference/2016/04/tomorrow-the-lord-will-do-wonders-among-you?lang=eng&amp;id=p19#p19\">Tomorrow the Lord Will Do Wonders Among You<\/a>,\u201d <cite>Ensign<\/cite> or <cite>Liahona<\/cite>, May 2016, 127).<\/p>",
